response.original_title: Airport For Birds (And Other Great Ideas)
response.overview: From the group that brought you "A Very Potter Musical" comes "Airport for Birds": an evening of "great" ideas and other bits that have hit the cutting room floor. Watch familiar StarKid faces fly through 90 minutes of sketch comedy and music, filmed live at The Second City's UP Comedy Club. Grab your bird-ing pass, the nearest unattended bag, and prepare for departure with "Airport For Birds (and Other Great Ideas)".
